WEBVTT

00:00:03.354 --> 00:00:12.062 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
How does it make you feel 
when you preach and teach with zeal,

00:00:12.062 --> 00:00:19.312 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
When you know you’ve done your part
to reach an honest heart?

00:00:21.895 --> 00:00:30.312 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Knowing you’ve done your best;
then our God will do the rest.

00:00:30.312 --> 00:00:39.062 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Honest hearts he surely knows—
all those to him disposed.

00:00:40.437 --> 00:00:49.437 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
How does it make you feel
when the words you speak appeal

00:00:49.437 --> 00:00:57.354 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
To the ones whose heart is right
for everlasting life?

00:00:59.020 --> 00:01:07.979 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Some people turn away,
others might be led astray.

00:01:07.979 --> 00:01:15.645 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Still we’re glad to bear his name
and witness just the same.

00:01:16.770 --> 00:01:26.270 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
It makes us glad, and we rejoice
to give our heart and mind and voice.

00:01:26.270 --> 00:01:35.145 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
So may our sacrifice of praise
continue all our days.

00:01:36.645 --> 00:01:45.395 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
How does it make you feel,
knowing God’s support is real,

00:01:45.395 --> 00:01:52.979 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And that he’s entrusted you
to do the work we do?

00:01:54.479 --> 00:02:03.770 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Proudly we preach and teach,
using bold but gracious speech,

00:02:03.770 --> 00:02:11.812 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Searching out deserving ones;
this work will soon be done.

00:02:12.937 --> 00:02:22.104 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
It makes us glad, and we rejoice
to give our heart and mind and voice.

00:02:22.104 --> 00:02:30.645 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
So may our sacrifice of praise
continue all our days.

